message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
type: software
title: "GROMACS Web UI: An LLM-Guided Web Interface for Autonomous MD Simulation"
abstract: >-
  A FastAPI + vanilla JS web application that uses LLM agents (Claude, Codex,
  or Gemini) to autonomously drive GROMACS molecular dynamics simulations
  from a single uploaded PDB file, via a skills-based pipeline (env-builder,
  md-runner, illustrator) with live command-execution transparency and
  tutorial-grounded guidance. Supports 8 tutorial systems including
  Lysozyme, KALP15 membrane, Protein-Ligand, Umbrella Sampling, and Free
  Energy Perturbation.
